text: Etty Fraser Martins de Sousa (8 May 1931 — 31 December 2018) was a Brazilian actress. She was born in Rio de Janeiro, Brazil. Her best known works include Beto Rockfeller, Durval Discos and Cristina Wants to Get Married.
